General.Name: Thrive Tribe Technologies Ltd.
General.Description: Thrive Tribe Technologies Limited, together with its subsidiaries, develops cloud-based Software-as-a-Service solutions that provides employee engagement solutions in Australia. The company operates in two segments, Wooboard Technologies and WooBoard Software as a Service Products. Its solutions include WooBoard, a peer-to-peer employee recognition platform. The company's solutions focus on mental health and wellbeing, skill building, and performance optimization of employees. It serves enterprises, employees, customers, and other supply chain stakeholders. The company was formerly known as Wooboard Technologies Limited and changed its name to Thrive Tribe Technologies Limited in April 2023. Thrive Tribe Technologies Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
